                            <comment id="12683579" author="erikholstad@gmail.com" created="Thu, 19 Mar 2009 19:40:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In the Store, when figuring out what storefiles to look in it is sometimes needed to fetch the families for that region first, to the&lt;br/&gt;
families for the GetQueries, so just made the keys from the map inside the HTableDescriptor visible to the outside.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12683581" author="erikholstad@gmail.com" created="Thu, 19 Mar 2009 19:41:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Uploaded first patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12683582" author="erikholstad@gmail.com" created="Thu, 19 Mar 2009 19:44:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch was created by diff the git version that Stack is working on, for the new server implementation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12683598" author="stack" created="Thu, 19 Mar 2009 20:23:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s URL to where I&apos;m doing the KeyValue &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1234&quot; title=&quot;Change HBase StoreKey format&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1234&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1234&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://github.com/ryanobjc/hbase/tree/stack&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://github.com/ryanobjc/hbase/tree/stack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12689378" author="apurtell" created="Thu, 26 Mar 2009 07:04:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The HTD currently in trunk uses Integers as keys for the &apos;families&apos; hashmap, not byte[]. Attached is a patch v2 that does what I think you want and compiles. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
